{"tid":2501271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警辯稱處理證物有遺漏「唔記得指引好正常」 官:是否要發傳票予鄧炳強出庭作供講解","createTime":"2021-04-23T08:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T09:17:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7f92c0ae0ef26f2d7add298ed3e45e5df5ed7a16","tid":2501271,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:55:30.000Z","msg":"警方去年4月在油麻地一間酒店進行打擊毒品行動，其間一名男子涉販運毒品被捕，被控販運危險藥物等5罪，案件今在區域法院審訊。毒品調查科警員作供期間，遭辯方揭發處理證物時諸多甩漏，包括在被告或他人不在場的情況下量度毒品，警員直認「有遺漏」、「有疏忽」。辯方質疑警員未有依循《警察通例》指引，警員直言「唔記得好正常」，法官葉佐文不禁問，是否要發傳票予警務處長出庭作供講解指引；又問警員毒品調查科總警司是誰，警員表示不記得。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今盤問警員8119黎志豪，指他在處理證物時諸多甩漏，包括沒有將在被告褲袋搜出、用作包裝毒品的利是封封存，或送往進行毒理化驗。黎同意，但不同意在現場拍攝證物時「影漏嘢」。辯方隨即揭發黎並無拍下該涉案利是封，多次質問黎是否犯錯，黎均無正面回應，只表示「部份同意（有錯失）」、「有遺漏」、「有疏忽」及「可以做得更好」。<br />\n<br />\n黎承認當日處理證物後沒向值日官報告，揚言「唔一定要我通知」；他又承認在被告不在場的情況下量度毒品重量，自言據他了解，毋須在被告在場下進行量度。他又承認，量度毒品時沒其他同事在場，事後亦沒作書面記錄，僅向案件主管口頭匯報，沒留意對方有否作出記錄。<br />\n<br />\n法官葉佐文明言，並非要求黎背出《警察通例》，但質疑黎理應記得相關處理證物的指引，又是否需要發傳票予警務處處長出庭講解；葉官另一度問毒品調查科總警司是誰，黎表示不記得。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210423/UOIDMMNVJ5GCLIH6PNRK6YIJPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210423%2FUOIDMMNVJ5GCLIH6PNRK6YIJPU%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=2e474d75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210423%2FUOIDMMNVJ5GCLIH6PNRK6YIJPU%2F&h=8686af5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210423/UOIDMMNVJ5GCLIH6PNRK6YIJPU/</a>"},{"pid":"9f2f319a4dae4cc3f9da8505d2f10c6b3b79f2bc","tid":2501271,"uid":33868,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:56:08.000Z","msg":"已經服用咗d毒品"},{"pid":"0f60bc4aef8a26ba00b69e0226a1f8a03b50c623","tid":2501271,"uid":4243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"好無紀律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大到你最大果個都仲係是是旦旦咁<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">好似自己仲重要過強仔咁</span></span>"},{"pid":"adbeee16bfa84f2ce1e76677ff29a43ace4ff5eb","tid":2501271,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑撚死"},{"pid":"76c1a92fe891a55ec86c7750f7f4cc0efae21506","tid":2501271,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"狗長不出象牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1a2c9596ca99ffe30caacd2d7e5d66699f5f68","tid":2501271,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f60bc4aef8a26ba00b69e0226a1f8a03b50c623","tid":2501271,"uid":4243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"好無紀律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大到你最大果個都仲係是是旦旦咁<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">好似自己仲重要過強仔咁</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"黑社會講紀律係咁上下"},{"pid":"d93cb2603525f3bec1f027fa8e2538dad830b187","tid":2501271,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:13:28.000Z","msg":"請傳召鄧PK"},{"pid":"1fd5ec0f75f12a9ccdeb2e38a8c38c3c6386caab","tid":2501271,"uid":188282,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">問警員毒品調查科總警司是誰，警員表示不記得</span><br />\n<br />\n講大話"},{"pid":"d70af743bea4c7b6379d9ddd5b20c2b6bed8b22c","tid":2501271,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:16:53.000Z","msg":"呢單係咪隻狗自己販毒嗰單?<br />\n又放生自己人"},{"pid":"70338782d521c593ad0dbd2277df7b908646270f","tid":2501271,"uid":251880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"